    "description": "Join the Zerodha Advisory Limited family as a Investment Banker in Srinagar. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Zerodha Advisory Limited:\nZerodha Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in VBA\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zerodha Advisory Limited!",
